1 term not to exceed thirty (30) days, and by a fine not less than
2 Fifty Dollars ($50.00) nor more than Five Hundred Dollars ($500.00);
3 2. For a third or subsequent conviction, in the event the value
4 of the goods, edible meat, or other corporeal property which has
5 been taken is less than One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00) Five
